      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THE ART OF SUCCESS (9) is a lightly-raced but progressive mare who made it two wins in a row at her latest appearance at Mildura, coming from wider on this row and racing up to four deep before scoring by 4.7 metres. Big chance to land the hat trick. KEAYANG SWEETHEART (11) led and proved far too good at her latest appearance at Bendigo, scoring by close to 9 metres. May need a bit of luck from a more challenging  draw but that latest win was her third from just four starts so she has plenty of upside. DELIGHTFUL CHARM (7) has clocked in second in her last two outings here. Draws wider and has had five weeks off but was kept up to the mark with a trial win. KIA ORA BEAUTY (4) could feature after chasing along the sprint lane for third at Bendigo last time out.",
